title: Keurig® 2.0 Brewing Different Beverages
description: Not all beverages are created equal.  This video will show you how to brew each Keurig® branded portion pack to make sure you get the best tasting beverage, everytime.The Keurig 2.0 brewing system is designed to brew K-Cup & K-Carafe packs.
